            <title>[FLINK-4436] Unclosed DataOutputBuffer in Utils#setTokensFor()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-4436</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    DataOutputBuffer dob = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; DataOutputBuffer();
    credentials.writeTokenStorageToStream(dob);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;dob should be closed upon returning from the method.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;YarnApplicationMasterRunner#createTaskManagerContext() has similar issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
